## 数据流架构

```
29个信源 → RSSCollector → PostgreSQL(intelligence表) → Redis PUBLISH
                                                              ↓
                                                       AlphaEngine(Worker)
                                                              ↓
                          ┌───────────────────────────────────┤
                          ↓                                   ↓
                    EventClusterer                      AI分析(DeepSeek/Gemini)
                    (pg_trgm聚类)                      含宏观上下文快照
                          ↓                                   ↓
                    NewsDeduplicator              intelligence.entities(JSONB)
                    (SimHash+pgvector)                   + relations
                                                              ↓
                                                    upsert_knowledge_graph
                                                    entity_nodes/entity_edges
                                                              ↓
                                              urgency≥7 → 推送(Bark/Email)
                    BacktestEngine ← 1h/4h后 ← COMPLETED
                    (价格回填+胜率统计)
```

